==Tailoring==
Beet can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Button Down Shirt]].  [[File:Shirt140.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a purple dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*10 Beets are needed for the 2nd part of [[Quests#The Mysterious Qi|"The Mysterious Qi" Quest]]

==Trivia==
The misspelling of "vegetable" in the beet's description appears in-game.

